---
title: Honey Garlic Chicken Tenders with Potatoes and Green Beans
description: Tonight, bring the best of pub grub to your table! Sweet honey and savoury garlic combine to create a wing-night-inspired glaze for chicken tenders. We've added garlicky green beans and roasted potatoes alongside for a wholesome twist.
